# Correlation coefficients
confy <- function(x){
  # fit <- lm(df$adjusted_stand_dif ~ x)
  r <- cor(df$adjusted_stand_dif, x,
           use = 'complete.obs')
  CIr(r=r, n = nrow(df), level = .95)
}
